Czech (/ tʃɛk /; čeština Czech waa: [tʃɛʃcɪna]), taariikh ahaan Bohemiyan [6] (boazhiːmiən, bə - /; [7] lingua Bohemica ee Laatiinka), waa luqada galbeedka Slavic ee kooxda Czech-Slovak. [6] In ka badan 10 milyan oo qof ayaa ku hadla, waxay u adeegtaa luqadda rasmiga ah ee Jamhuuriyadda Czech. Czech wuxuu si dhow ula xiriiraa Slovakka, ilaa heerka caqli-galnimada si aad u heer sareeya. [8] Sida luqadaha kale ee Slavic, Czech waa luuqad fool-ka-fool ah oo leh nidaam hodan ah oo miro-dhalineed iyo amar erey oo rogrogmi kara. Erayada waxaa si weyn u saameeyay Latin [9] iyo Jarmal. [10]
